      "properties": {
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "ONE LOGO IN, A FULL BRAND KIT OUT\n\nTakes one logo and produces: a transparent export, square + banner\nversions, a monochrome silhouette, an icon/square/banner export pack\nat custom sizes, and a legibility check showing how it holds up at\nfavicon scale.\n\nFlow: Load Image -> Mask Adapter -> Trim, then three branches:\n  1. Logo Asset Builder -> 4x (Mask Adapter -> Join Image With Alpha\n     -> Save Image) for transparent/square/banner/monochrome.\n  2. Asset Pack Export -> Save Image (runs once per requested size\n     automatically -- see its README entry on OUTPUT_IS_LIST).\n  3. Thumbnail Legibility Check -> Preview Image.\n\nSet before running:\n  - Load Image: your own logo (transparent background works best)\n  - Logo Asset Builder: square_size / banner_width / banner_height /\n    monochrome_color\n  - Asset Pack Export 'sizes': add/remove \"label:WxH\" entries,\n    comma- or newline-separated\n  - Thumbnail Legibility Check 'sizes': the preview sizes to compare"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653",
      "title": "README"
    },
